#: apps/channel/template_message.py:17
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Congratulations! You've earned {amount} for successfully referring a friend "
"to our app. The money has been added to your wallet."
msgstr ""
"تهانينا! لقد حصلت على {amount} لإحالتك صديقًا بنجاح إلى تطبيقنا. تم إضافة "
"المبلغ إلى محفظتك."

#: apps/channel/template_message.py:20
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"A new customer has joined through your referral! You've earned {amount} "
"which has been added to your wallet."
msgstr ""
"انضم عميل جديد عبر رابط الإحالة الخاص بك! لقد حصلت على {amount} وتمت إضافته "
"إلى محفظتك."

#: apps/channel/template_message.py:25
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Great news! Your referred friend has placed their first order. You've earned "
"{amount} as a referral bonus!"
msgstr ""
"أخبار رائعة! صديقك الذي أحلته قد قدم أول طلب له. لقد حصلت على {amount} "
"كمكافأة إحالة!"

#: apps/channel/template_message.py:28
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Your referred customer has completed their first order! You've been rewarded "
"{amount} for the successful referral."
msgstr ""
"لقد أتم العميل الذي أحلته طلبه الأول! تم مكافأتك بمبلغ {amount} مقابل "
"الإحالة الناجحة."

